description: Two brand new wrestlers join the ranks this week. Sebastian Keys is a three-time black belt and brings a level headed confidence to his fighting style. Tommy Defendi doesn't have nearly the same experience but he's got plenty enough attitude to not care how much training his opponent has. Tommy is taller and bigger than his opponent, and he's just eager to fuck Sebastian with his nine inch cock. Size or skills, you'll be the judge.
title: Sebastian Keys vs. Tommy Defendi
